INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS FOR WINDOWS

1) Download Ruby for Windows (Under 12MB) from:

http://rubyforge.org/frs/download.php/73722/rubyinstaller-1.9.2-p136.exe

2) Once it is installed, then download this source. The .rb files should be associated with ruby.exe in your Ruby/bin folder. If not, create the association.

3) Double click on a file named *_executable.rb and enjoy!

